 class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聖經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79461edda40ebd8633e26b3188947b189088f97","tid":2262964,"uid":69022,"like":99,"dislike":16,"score":83,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T13:38:36.000Z","msg":"最後一題打大佬：宗教無強迫。正道與迷路確已分明了。<br />\n可蘭經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聖經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d2b79c82a77ac431e394639cb9051066892100","tid":2262964,"uid":5523,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T13:39:40.000Z","msg":"答: 全部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後一題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 聖經之鬼"},{"pid":"307a984e93cb828e50627dc8393f9776a7c54814","tid":2262964,"uid":42735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T13:40:32.000Z","msg":"2121211222<br />\n答案呢"},{"pid":"7c77c74b6f46315de7f6add0394cc7a52e5e7516","tid":2262964,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a79461edda40ebd8633e26b3188947b189088f97","tid":2262964,"uid":69022,"like":99,"dislike":16,"score":83,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T13:38:36.000Z","msg":"最後一題打大佬：宗教無強迫。正道與迷路確已分明了。<br />\n可蘭經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聖經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T13:41:14.000Z","msg":"我估可蘭經"},{"pid":"dc180071b807bff1d76c92a3224579329a9e1fca","tid":2262964,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T13:42:14.000Z","msg":"2212111121"},{"pid":"8b6c1088aee51f55320b681e26e6bbdeeb13d3fd","tid":2262964,"uid":69022,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T13:44:08.000Z","msg":"answer:<br />\n<br />\n你的兩乳、好像百合花中喫草的一對小鹿、就是母鹿雙生的。<br />\n聖經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俗語說得真不錯：「狗所吐的，牠轉過來又吃；豬洗淨了，又回到泥裡去滾。」這話在他們身上正合式。<br />\n聖經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n姦夫只可娶淫婦，或拜偶像的女子。<br />\n可蘭經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人若引誘沒有受聘的處女，與她行淫，他總要交出聘禮，娶她為妻。<br />\n聖經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你們怎麼做那種醜事(同性戀)呢？在你們之前，全世界的人沒有一個做過這種事的。<br />\n可蘭經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你們的妻室就像是你們的田地，你們願意時就可進入你們的田地。<br />\n可蘭經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n那精液是從脊柱和肋骨之間發出的。<br />\n可蘭經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n他們問你月經的（律例），你說：「月經是有害的，故在經期中你們應當離開妻子，不要與她們交接，直到她們清潔。當她們洗淨的時候，你們可以在(耶和華/真主)所命你們的部位與她們交接。」(耶和華/真主)的確喜愛悔罪的人，的確喜愛潔淨的人。<br />\n可蘭經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你若背著丈夫行了污穢的事，在你丈夫以外有人與你行淫，(耶和華/真主) 叫你大腿消瘦，肚腹發脹，使你在你民中被人咒詛，成了誓語<br />\n聖經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宗教無強迫。正道與迷路確已分明了。<br />\n可蘭經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可蘭經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cab05971b0d877a448e5784b4c294ff24da19f2","tid":2262964,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T13:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f45a3433e470be89637771464a57f45f6956d1","tid":2262964,"uid":69022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T13:54:14.000Z","msg":"-完-"},{"pid":"3cc1fe8809480aa0b707a243be0c4ad6ba3ea2a7","tid":2262964,"uid":181156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T00:25:44.000Z","msg":"冇佛經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd14f3e4c34d861b41a76db16aa059a30c438d05","tid":2262964,"uid":85131,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T00:33:59.000Z","msg":"王回答迦勒底人說：夢我已經忘了（或譯：我已定命；八節同），你們若不將夢和夢的講解